### Insights API Test Suite
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000/insights
### Auth: Bearer token required (Clerk JWT)

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = your_clerk_jwt_token_here

### 1. Get trend forecasts (30/60/90 days)
POST {{baseUrl}}/insights/forecast
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "metrics": ["engagement", "followers", "clicks"],
  "period": "30d"
}

### Example Response:
### [
###   {
###     "metric": "engagement",
###     "currentValue": 1000,
###     "trend": "increasing",
###     "predictions": [
###       {
###         "date": "2025-11-08",
###         "value": 1200,
###         "confidence": 85,
###         "range": { "min": 1100, "max": 1300 }
###       }
###     ],
###     "confidence": 80,
###     "factors": ["Consistent posting schedule", "High engagement rate"]
###   }
### ]

### 2. Get AI-generated insights
GET {{baseUrl}}/insights?limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Example Response:
### [
###   {
###     "type": "opportunity",
###     "title": "Leverage trending audio",
###     "description": "Your niche has 3 trending audio tracks with 10M+ uses",
###     "impact": "high",
###     "confidence": 85,
###     "actionableSteps": [
###       "Create content using trending audio #1",
###       "Post within next 48 hours while trending"
###     ],
###     "relatedMetrics": ["engagement", "reach"]
###   }
### ]

### 3. Predict viral potential
POST {{baseUrl}}/insights/viral
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Behind the scenes of how we built our product! Watch till the end for a surprise 👀",
  "contentType": "video",
  "platform": "tiktok"
}

### Example Response:
### {
###   "score": 82,
###   "probability": 15,
###   "estimatedReach": { "min": 50000, "max": 200000 },
###   "factors": [
###     {
###       "factor": "Strong hook in first 3 seconds",
###       "impact": 30,
###       "description": "Grabs attention immediately"
###     },
###     {
###       "factor": "Behind-the-scenes content",
###       "impact": 25,
###       "description": "High engagement in your niche"
###     }
###   ],
###   "recommendations": [
###     "Post during peak hours (6-9 PM)",
###     "Use trending audio for 2x boost",
###     "Add text overlay for accessibility"
###   ]
### }

### 4. Get content gap analysis
GET {{baseUrl}}/insights/gaps
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Example Response:
### {
###   "missingTopics": [
###     "Behind-the-scenes content",
###     "Product tutorials",
###     "Customer success stories"
###   ],
###   "opportunityAreas": [
###     {
###       "area": "Educational content",
###       "potential": 85,
###       "competition": "medium",
###       "recommendations": [
###         "Create how-to guides",
###         "Share expert tips",
###         "Answer common questions"
###       ]
###     }
###   ],
###   "underservedAudiences": [
###     "Beginners in your niche",
###     "Advanced users looking for tips"
###   ]
### }

### 5. Get optimal posting times
GET {{baseUrl}}/insights/times?platform=instagram&timezone=America/New_York
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Example Response:
### {
###   "recommendedTimes": [
###     {
###       "day": "Monday",
###       "time": "09:00 AM",
###       "confidence": 85,
###       "reason": "Peak morning engagement for professionals"
###     },
###     {
###       "day": "Wednesday",
###       "time": "02:00 PM",
###       "confidence": 80,
###       "reason": "Afternoon break time, high scroll activity"
###     }
###   ],
###   "timezone": "America/New_York"
### }

### 6. Get audience growth prediction
GET {{baseUrl}}/insights/growth?platform=instagram
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Example Response:
### {
###   "currentFollowers": 1000,
###   "predictedGrowth": {
###     "30d": 1200,
###     "60d": 1500,
###     "90d": 2000
###   },
###   "growthRate": 20,
###   "trend": "steady",
###   "recommendations": [
###     "Post 3-5x per week for consistent growth",
###     "Engage with comments within first hour",
###     "Use trending hashtags in your niche",
###     "Collaborate with similar accounts"
###   ]
### }

### Full workflow example
### Step 1: Get forecasts
# @name getForecasts
POST {{baseUrl}}/insights/forecast
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "metrics": ["engagement", "followers"],
  "period": "30d"
}

### Step 2: Check viral potential before posting
POST {{baseUrl}}/insights/viral
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Your amazing content here",
  "contentType": "video",
  "platform": "tiktok"
}

### Step 3: Get best posting time
GET {{baseUrl}}/insights/times?platform=tiktok&timezone=UTC
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


